The paper discusses the learning dynamics of convolutional neural networks in the context of image classification, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on the learning dynamics of CNNs, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
